do npm install first to dynamically load all libraries.
both directives are used in app.component.html
1) appHighlight custom directive
  --changes style.background property of host html/custom element using appHighlight custom
  directive. It also listens to dom events click,mouse over and mouse out
2) appChangeColor custom directive
 --changes style.fontSize and value propert of host input element using the appChangeColor custome
      directive. it also listesns to mouseover event to change the value and fontsize dom properties.
